						 <p>This may be a weird suggestion but why wouldn't a deliberate secondary containment measure made from lots and lots of microorgansims be constructed just in case the power on the electromagnet fails?</p> <p>It would certainly stall the SCP out as it tried to leave while techs could work on restoring the power.</p> <p>You could even use yeast to brew beer in there or farm mushrooms. It's a win-win situation!</p> 
